Name: WaterQualityAssessor
Version: 0.0.2
Summary: Assess the toxicity levels of various trace metals according to EPA MCL standards in post-wildfire habitat watersheds
Home-page: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/WaterQualityAssessor/
Author: Megan Maccagnan
Author-email: meganmaccagnan@mines.edu
License: LICENSE.txt
Platform: UNKNOWN
